PersonalMission.Name: TD-14: Big Hunt
PersonalMission.Description: A well-coordinated Platoon of tank destroyers will not allow the enemy to outflank their team's positions. This mission may be completed either as part of a Platoon or on your own, however, the latter is more difficult.
PersonalMission.Hint: Provide covering fire for members of your Platoon who have taken a beating. Sometimes it is better to draw enemy fire yourself in order to give an ally a chance to retreat to safety.

Primary.Conditions:
Cause 25% of the total amount of damage caused by your team
  Win
